# shapedArrayValue(of:)

**Instance Method**

Returns the shaped array value, if the contained value is a shaped array of the specified type.

## Declaration

```swift
func shapedArrayValue<Scalar>(of type: Scalar.Type) -> MLShapedArray<Scalar>? where Scalar : MLShapedArrayScalar
```
